          <div class="card-fro">
            <img src="images/icons8-falling-man-48.png" alt="Fall Detection Icon" class="project-icon">
            <h3>Fall Detection Device</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="card-bac">
            <p>Developed a smart IoT-based wearable using ESP32, MPU6050, and BLE to detect elderly falls in real-time. Enabled Bluetooth alerts, OTA firmware updates, deep sleep mode, and battery monitoring. Integrated motion sensing, status LEDs, and remote deployment features for a reliable, low-power, and user-friendly elderly safety solution.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-inn">
          <div class="card-fro">
            <img src="images/icons8-chat.gif" alt="Fall Detection Icon" class="project-icon">
            <h3>Real Time Chat App(Java)</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="card-bac">
            <p>Built a real-time chat system using Java Swing and socket programming with a one-client-one-server architecture. Designed a clean and responsive UI for smooth messaging. Focused on real-time communication, efficient data transfer, and intuitive message alignment (sender-right, receiver-left). This project strengthened my skills in Java networking, GUI design, and client-server architecture.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-inn">
          <div class="card-fro">
            <img src="images/icons8-analytics.gif" alt="Fall Detection Icon" class="project-icon">
            <h3>Airline Data Analytics</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="card-bac">
            <p>Created key KPIs like average delay time, cancellation rate, and on-time performance. Designed visually engaging dashboards in Qlik Sense using bar charts, pie charts, line graphs, and filters. These dashboards allowed real-time interaction and trend analysis, helping to identify critical performance metrics and improve data-driven decisions.</p>
